制度下既香港法律係唔撚work既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女事主嫁比台灣人呀<br />\n唔係女事主係台妹</blockquote><br />\n以為我睇錯，邊度黎個台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6554b73aac0819552c9c3b5339e4c10004904c50","tid":381830,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:23:25.000Z","msg":"全女班居然pass"},{"pid":"faa13facb6ea3926891edd60443df45f6b51a8d0","tid":381830,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  男要出全名</blockquote><br />\n真係唔撚明<br />\n點解比人屈嗰個要出全名<br />\n屈人嗰個就可以隱姓埋名</blockquote><br />\n唔驚比女權撚屌咩"},{"pid":"f3f0a3c283b493e8bb803afefabf5bc6db5f1404","tid":381830,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全女班居然pass</blockquote><br />\n因為佢地應該覺得條女做第三者罪無可恕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d200d5cfec33fdba01979df6586578417be6c2","tid":381830,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"條港囡係仆街架啦，但個男人都衰啦有老婆仔女偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條台柒幫人養埋便宜仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}